thread.title: BRIEF-Edenbrook Capital Reports 5.37 Pct Stake In Telaria As Of March 5 - SEC Filing

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Edenbrook Capital Reports 5.37 Pct Stake In Telaria As Of March 5 - SEC Filing
text:
March 7 (Reuters) - Telaria Inc:
* EDENBROOK CAPITAL LLC REPORTS A 5.37 PERCENT STAKE IN TELARIA INC AS OF MARCH 5 - SEC FILING
* EDENBROOK CAPITAL SAYS ACQUIRED TELARIA SHARES “FOR INVESTMENT‍​”
* EDENBROOK CAPITAL SAYS HAVE ENGAGED, EXPECT TO CONTINUE TO ENGAGE IN, DISCUSSIONS WITH MEMBERS OF MANAGEMENT, BOARD OF TELARIA
* EDENBROOK CAPITAL SAYS TELARIA DISCUSSIONS REGARDING VARIETY OF MATTERS INCLUDING BOARD COMPOSITION, STRATEGIC ALTERNATIVES, AMONG OTHERS Source text: [ bit.ly/2FwEKi9 ] Further company coverage:
